Requirements
------------
In order to build Jamon from source, you need the following software:

* Ant 1.5.1 or above, including the optional tasks (for JUnit)
  http://ant.apache.org

* SableCC 2.16.2 and the SableCC Ant task 1.1.0
  http://www.sablecc.org

* JDK 1.3.1 or above

* JUnit 3.8 or above
  http://www.junit.org


Instructions
------------

1. Unpackage (tar or zip) the source distribution.

2. In the top-level directory, create a build.properties file that
   sets the following properties to point to the appropriate jar files:

  java.lib.junit
  java.lib.sablecc
  java.lib.sablecctask

3. From inside the top-level directory, execute

  ant jar

4. To run the integration tests:

  ant test
